name: printspoofer
help: Abuse SeImpersonatePrivilege or SeDebugPrivilege for SYSTEM escalation.
long_help:
Usage: printspoofer <command>

This BOF achieving SYSTEM escalation using two methods:
1. Print Spooler Named Pipe (SeImpersonate)
2. Token Stealing from user-mode processes (SeDebug)

The command is executed as SYSTEM and output is captured.
